# Stremio 3 install script for linux
 

Script downloads stremio 3.6.5 and install it in /opt folder creating the desktop and icon files



## Installation

Ubuntu:

```sh
git clone https://github.com/skypce/stremio-3-installer-script.git
```
```sh

chmod +x install.sh
```
```sh
sudo ./install.sh
```
## Usage example

The script will create the application launcher in /usr/share/applications, you can find it in the AudioVideo, Player or Video category. Stremio 3, works fine and do not sleep the screen.
